    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: February 27, 2024</p>
    
    <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
    <p>This tool only accesses and stores the necessary social media tokens and credentials required for posting content to your social media accounts.</p>
    
    <h2>2. Data Usage</h2>
    <p>The collected data is used solely for the purpose of scheduling and posting content to your social media accounts.</p>
    
    <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All data is stored locally and is not shared with any third parties.</p>
    
    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This tool interfaces with Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok APIs. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for information about how they handle your data.</p>
    
    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy-related questions, please contact the developer.</p>
